rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0002
rows.name:
So this is Gula. It's
beautiful, so green.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Which is exactly why so many
countries are after it. Such
a sad state of affairs.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0005
rows.name:
However, there was
likely nowhere else...

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0006
rows.name:
a place where Laura-sama's
mother could settle down.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0007
rows.name: Don't make that kind of face, Kasumi.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0008
rows.name:
You already helped so much just by
finding out where Mom fled to.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Come on, let's hurry to Torigo. I
want to see Mom as soon as possible.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0011
rows.name: Right. It's just up this road.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0012
rows.name:
But this is unfamiliar
territory. Don't overdo it...

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]No, I suppose I can't really say that.

rows.label: fev11_170_150_msg0014
rows.name: I agree. Let's hurry, but be careful.
